From: Yifei Sun <ysun@hey.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Mar 2026 16:31:14 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add nix-darwin (macOS) deployment support

Merged on top of detached-activation patch.
Based on zhaofengli/colmena#319.
---
